          "description": "As an action, touch a willing creature to give it advantage on Dexterity (Stealth) checks. Lasts 1 hour or until you use this feature again.",
          "level": 1,
          "name": "Blessing of the Trickster",
          "source": "subclass",
        },
        {
          "description": "Always-prepared domain spells (they don't count against your prepared total): Charm Person, Disguise Self (L3); Mirror Image, Pass without Trace (L3); Blink, Dispel Magic (L5); Dimension Door, Polymorph (L7); Dominate Person, Modify Memory (L9).",
          "level": 1,
          "name": "Domain Spells",
