          "name": "Exceptional Training",
          "source": "subclass",
        },
        {
          "description": "Moving through nonmagical difficult terrain costs no extra movement. You can pass through nonmagical plants without being slowed or taking damage. Advantage on saves against magically created or manipulated plants.",
