          "description": "Choose one: Evasion (no damage on successful Dex save, half on failure); Stand Against the Tide (redirect a missed melee attack to another creature within range); or Uncanny Dodge (halve damage from one attack per reaction).",
          "level": 15,
          "name": "Superior Hunter's Defense",
          "source": "subclass",
        },
        {
          "description": "When not blinded or deafened, you are aware of invisible creatures within 30 ft even if they are hidden. In combat, no disadvantage on attacks against invisible creatures within 30 ft.",
          "level": 18,
          "name": "Feral Senses",
          "source": "class",
        },
      ],
