          "level": 6,
          "name": "Malleable Illusions",
          "source": "subclass",
        },
        {
          "description": "When a creature makes an attack roll against you, use your reaction to interpose an illusory duplicate — the attack automatically misses. Once used, you regain this ability on a short or long rest.",
